@gillianoberholzer  @shaunviljoen 

The last point in the above list is a bit tricky as Shaun, Stefan and myself got the process to work like this as the Person registering the company does not always have a Sales person as a referrer. As discussed previously, the Referrer is to be used as the Sales Person which is how it was spec'd previously.

Please also note that we created a Report for Chantelle in Report Central that checks for companies without Sales Persons and she assigns them for Commission purposes.

Please communicate this change with Chantelle as well please.
Please don't make a hasty decision with this change until all parties understand the current process and what will be affected if changed as requested in the checklist above.

@lungisaximbi
